seo: CVE-2017-7269, IIS远程代码执行漏洞, 漏洞检测
seo_en: CVE-2017-7269, IIS RCE vulnerability, vulnerability detection
summary: 该插件用于检测目标是否存在CVE-2017-7269 IIS远程代码执行漏洞，通过发送特定payload并分析返回数据来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the target has the CVE-2017-7269 IIS Remote Code Execution vulnerability by sending a specific payload and analyzing the returned data to confirm the existence of the vulnerability.
